    "name": "Create: Misc and Things",
    "summary": "üîß Add useful and fun things to Create",
    "description": "&nbsp;\n\n![Logo](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/816/96/logo_copie.png)\n\n\n[![Discord Logo](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/816/82/midlediscord_logo_copie.png)](https://discord.gg/3AvrppcgG3)\n\n[![Donate](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/e79bfe6b479f2a23fad07b79b13d88d027ae422e.png)](https://to0pa.ovh/donate)~~~~\n\n\n\n[![BH_NU_PROMO](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/816/78/bh_nu_promo.png)](https://bisecthosting.com/wrench)\n\n&nbsp;\n\n**Create: misc and things add some utility, building, and fun small things that don't fit in a theme. Gun made with a spout, Train Station Speaker, Building blocks...**\n\n&nbsp;\n\n# **__New Glue making method__ :**\n\n![Glue](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/816/95/glu.png)\n\n# **__Spout Gun__ :**\n\nUse Spout Gun to shoot liquid to your enemies!\n\n![Gun](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/816/94/gun.png)\n\n# **__Cards__ :**\n\nPut a Card in a card inscriber and make unique cards: scripted card can't be reproduced by other players. Use the Card Reader to validate your card!\n\n‚ö†Ô∏èCards can't be faked by another player because the player name is registered too\n\n![Card Reader](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/816/93/cardreader.png)\n\n# **__Speaker__ :**\n\nThe speaker does a sound and sends a custom message in the chat. The perfect block for a train station!\n\n![Speaker](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/816/100/speaker.png)\n\n# **__Traffic Signs__ :**\n\nDecorate your train tracks and avoid accidents!\n\n![Traffic Signs](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/816/99/sing.png)\n\n# **__Sticky Launchers__ :**\n\nJump like a rabbit! Use a sticker to craft the Copper Launcher and a Copper Launcher to craft the Brass Launcher!\n\n![Launchers](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/816/98/jfyhuhjkgukge.png)\n\n# **__Misc blocks__ :**\n\nNeon tube: Throwable Torch, allows you to explore caves and decorate your builds! Powdered Obsidian block: Breakable with a Diamond Shovel, perfect for a trap!\n\n![Misc Blocks](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/816/97/tub.png)\n\n# **__Misc items__ :**\n\nCrushed Magma: Good fuel source, cook 12 items. Slime Porridge: Right-click a Slime with this to make it grow. Portable Whistle: Station Masters need this!\n\n![Misc Items](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/816/102/rune.png)\n\n# **Magnifying Glass:**\n\nPut a card in your second hand and use the Magnifying Glass to see the script of a card.\n\n# **Vibration Mechanism:**\n\nUsed in crafts for new items.\n\n# **Mending Rune:**\n\nRepair all items with the mending enchantment. The mending rune takes XP from your XP bar to repair items.\n\n![Rune](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/816/103/ouikk.png)\n\n&nbsp;\n\n# **__Building Blocks__ :**\n\n![Building Blocks](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/816/101/tdrgffgfge.png)\n\nYou can put this mod in your modpack.\n\nInstall [jei](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/jei?adlt=strict&amp;toWww=1&amp;redig=8B55853145EB479E8CF26422E7C5851D) to see all the recipes.\n\nA question? Join the [discord](https://discord.gg/3AvrppcgG3)!\n\nIcon by Facu",
