    "slug": "create-ultimate-factory",
    "name": "Create: Ultimate Factory [Forge/Fabric/NeoForge]",
    "summary": "An addon for the Create mod developed to increase automation possibilities, adding 25 (reasonably) balanced recipes to the game.",
    "description": "<p>For 1.18.2 and older, refer to the <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/create-ultimate-factory-datapack\">datapack version</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/RHWfprW/banner5.png\" width=\"1125\" height=\"422\" /></p>\n<h2>About</h2>\n<p>Create: Ultimate Factory&nbsp;is a simple Create addon that introduces new automation possibilities. Through 25 new (reasonably) balanced recipes, this mod essentially makes dozens of Minecraft resources renewable.</p>\n<p>For example, Tuff is now renewable, giving players a reliable source of Ores and Experience. Lapis Lazuli, Amethyst, Redstone... Almost all resources are can now be automated. This also includes rare items and loot, at a much lower rate.</p>\n<p>Ever dreamt of automating Diamond or Netherite? It's now possible!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/sWkW5b6/Automate-Diamond.png\" alt=\"Automate Diamond from Coal Blocks and Lava with the Create Mod\" width=\"1125\" height=\"590\" /></p>\n<h2>Media</h2>\n<p><em>Compacting and Mixing recipes:</em><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/LD8WnZSx/compacting-mixing1.png\" width=\"1685\" height=\"676\" /></p>\n<p><em>More Compacting and Mixing recipes:</em><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/rRJDvZ4D/compacting-mixing2.png\" width=\"1685\" height=\"676\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<em>Haunting and Splashing recipes:</em><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/mrLHqPSm/haunting.png\" width=\"1694\" height=\"490\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<em>Crushing recipes:</em><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/B2BX8CPf/crushing-1.png\" width=\"1685\" height=\"992\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<em>More Crushing recipes:</em><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/84tnpVZV/crushing-2.png\" width=\"1685\" height=\"324\" /></p>\n<h2>Full recipe list (2.2.0+)</h2>\n<details>\n<summary>Show spoiler</summary>\n<p>Compacting<br />- Cobblestone and Lava to Tuff<br />- Stone and Lava to Deepslate<br />- Coal Blocks and Lava to Diamond (must be heated by an active Blaze Burner)<br />- Gravel and Bone Meal to Calcite<br />- Zinc Nuggets, Gravel and Water to Asurine<br />- Iron Nuggets, Gravel and Lava to Crimsite<br />- Gold Nuggets, Gravel and Lava to Ochrum<br />- Copper Nuggets, Gravel and Lava to Veridium<br />- Blaze Powder and Lava to Blaze Rod</p>\n<p>Mixing<br />- Netherrack, Flint and Lava to Redstone<br />- Calcite and Water to Dripstone<br />- Coal and Blaze Powder to Gunpowder</p>\n<p>Haunting<br />- Basalt to Netherrack<br />- Obsidian to Crying Obsidian<br />- Charcoal to Coal<br />- Poppy to Wither Rose</p>\n<p>Splashing<br />- Packed Ice to Blue Ice<br />- Magma Cream to Slime Ball</p>\n<p>Crushing<br />- Blackstone to Wither Skull (rare), occasionaly gives back Blackstone<br />- Scoria to Blaze Dust and Blaze Rod (rare)<br />- Nether Bricks to Nether Brick and Netherite Scraps (extremely rare)<br />- Soul Sand to Glowstone Dust<br />- Limestone to Quartz and Lapis Lazuli<br />- Red Sandstone to Red Sand and Nautilus Shell (extremely rare)<br />- Sea Grass to Sea Pickle (rare) and Eye of the Sea (extremely rare), occasionaly gives back Sea Grass<br />- Crying Obsidian to Powdered Obsidian and Amethyst Shard<br />- Endstone to Ender Pearl (rare), occasionaly gives back Endstone</p>\n</details>\n<h2>Videos</h2>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/y86ZMhsaiu8?si=VhQL_9osGb-tX-AY&amp;amp\" height=\"315\" width=\"560\"></iframe> <iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/UMCJcBKiuMc\" height=\"315\" width=\"560\"></iframe> <iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/jKi9NfJOuyk?si=QWfjMlJtUvLD-aqj\" height=\"315\" width=\"560\"></iframe> <iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4WkfkDNcIM0?si=9LbwyZ1T4SQ_1KHc\" height=\"315\" width=\"560\"></iframe> <iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/S7b3scOXKf4?si=Hng0T1dDrF7mvdYv&amp;amp\" height=\"315\" width=\"560\"></iframe> <iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/N7kxzI5BRO0?si=mMJXUg8Vu922PDHL\" height=\"315\" width=\"560\"></iframe> <iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/eUcTwX7f82s?si=lwFVuxqI_4fg6Q0L\" height=\"315\" width=\"560\"></iframe> <iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://youtube.com/embed/HT5udzd62wg?si=XcKo9qdMva2yI7iq\" height=\"315\" width=\"560\"></iframe> <iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/7L99ti217mA?si=2_br6Noqsdv1MOPV\" height=\"315\" width=\"560\"></iframe></p>\n<h2>Dependencies</h2>\n<p>Only the base <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/create\">Create</a>&nbsp;mod is&nbsp;required for the above recipes to work.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/jei\">JEI</a> is recommended but not required.</p>\n<h2>Installation</h2>\n<p>Add the .jar mod file into your mods&nbsp;folder.</p>\n<p>Alternatively, you can browse the Modrinth launcher for the mod (if it doesn't show up, try typing the autor's name). Once found, click \"Install\" to add it to your modpack.</p>\n<h2>Permissions</h2>\n<p>You are free to include this mod in any modpack, public or private.</p>\n<h2>Support my work</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/vL9gzRz/image.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"20\" /> <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/robinfrt/projects\"><strong>Download my projects on CurseForge</strong></a><br /> <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/FY9Qzzy/favicon-V2.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/robinfrt\"><strong>Download my projects on Modrinth</strong></a><br /> <img src=\"https://tinyurl.com/ffeam6b7\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /> <a href=\"https://www.paypal.com/donate/?hosted_button_id=XZ22AETPTQBD4\"><strong>Donate on Paypal</strong></a></p>",
