    "summary": "Adds a button to the statistics screen to export data to a text file.",
    "description": "<!--suppress HtmlDeprecatedAttribute HtmlDeprecatedTag, XmlDeprecatedElement -->\n<div align=\"center\"><center>\n\n<!--suppress CheckImageSize -->\n<img alt=\"Icon\" width=100 src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/TerminalMC/ExportStats/HEAD/common/src/main/resources/assets/exportstats/icon.png\">\n\n## ExportStats\n\nAdds a button to the statistics screen to export data to a text file.\n\n[![Environment](https://img.shields.io/badge/Environment-Client-blue?logo=data:image/png;base64,)]()\n[![Latest Minecraft](https://img.shields.io/modrinth/game-versions/kyhaDyaG?label=Latest%20Minecraft&color=%2300AF5C&logo=data:image/png;base64,)](https://modrinth.com/mod/kyhaDyaG/versions)\n\n[![Loader](https://img.shields.io/badge/Available%20for-Fabric-dbd0b4?logo=data:image/png;base64,)](https://fabricmc.net)\n[![Loader](https://img.shields.io/badge/Available%20for-Forge%201.20.1-1d2d41?logo=data:image/png;base64,)](https://files.minecraftforge.net)\n[![Loader](https://img.shields.io/badge/Available%20for-NeoForge%201.21%2B-f16436?logo=data:image/png;base64,)](https://neoforged.net)\n\n[![Download on Modrinth](https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/kyhaDyaG?label=Download%20on%20Modrinth&logo=modrinth&logoColor=%2300AF5C)](https://modrinth.com/mod/kyhaDyaG)\n[![Download on CurseForge](https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/1306453?label=Download%20on%20CurseForge&logo=curseforge)](https://curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/exportstats)\n[![Download on GitHub](https://img.shields.io/github/downloads/TerminalMC/ExportStats/total?label=Download%20on%20GitHub&logo=github&logoColor=white)](https://github.com/TerminalMC/ExportStats)\n\n</center></div>\n\n### About\n\nSimply click the relevant button and your statistics will be exported to a file for later viewing.\n\n<table style=\"width:100%;\">\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"width:50%;\"><img alt=\"In-game statistics screen\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/TerminalMC/ExportStats/HEAD/assets/images/ingame_01.png\" style=\"width:100%;\"></td>\n    <td style=\"width:50%;\"><img alt=\"Exported data files\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/TerminalMC/ExportStats/HEAD/assets/images/files_01.png\" style=\"width:100%;\"></td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n- File contents are translated according to your in-game language.\n- When you click the export button, a new folder (named for the world or server that you are\n  currently in) is created in the `.minecraft/config/exportstats` folder, and the data files are\n  placed in the created folder.\n- If you click the export button again while in the same world or server, the old files will be\n  replaced with new ones.\n\n### Related\n\n- [SearchStats](https://modrinth.com/mod/ExI7GmJi) by TerminalMC\n  - Adds a search bar to the statistics screen to quickly find specific entries.\n- [Better Statistics Screen](https://modrinth.com/mod/n6PXGAoM) by TheCSDev\n  - Completely overhauls the statistics screen and makes it more useful.\n\n### Contact\n\n[![Discord](https://img.shields.io/discord/1103153365216669797?logo=discord&label=Discord%20Server&color=%235865F2)](https://discord.terminalmc.dev)\n\n[![Issues](https://img.shields.io/github/issues/TerminalMC/ExportStats?logo=github&label=GitHub%20Issues)](https://github.com/TerminalMC/ExportStats/issues)\n\n[![License](https://img.shields.io/github/license/TerminalMC/ExportStats?label=License&logo=github&logoColor=white)](https://github.com/TerminalMC/ExportStats/blob/HEAD/LICENSE.txt)",
