    "slug": "exposure-polaroid",
    "name": "Exposure: Polaroid",
    "summary": "Addon for Exposure that adds Instant Camera",
    "description": "<br>\n<div align=\"center\">\n<img alt=\"Polaroid\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mortuusars/resources/main/media/exposure_polaroid/main-512.png\" alt=\"Exposure Polaroid\" width=225/>\n</div>\n<br>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  \n### Addon for [Exposure](https://modrinth.com/mod/exposure) that adds Instant Camera<br><br>\n\n<img alt=\"Polaroid\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mortuusars/resources/main/media/exposure_polaroid/page_instant_camera.png\" alt=\"Description\"/>\n\n</div>\n<br>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Description in text form</summary>\n\n**Instant Camera** operates largely in the same way as a regular Camera, but exposes **Instant Slides** instead of a Film roll.\n- As with Film rolls, there are color slides as well as black and white.\n- To load the slides, right click the camera item with them in inventory.\n- Camera can hold up to **12** slides.\n- When exposed, you'll get your Photograph in 2 seconds. No developing needed.\n- Single slide produces one Photograph. \n \n\nSince **Instant Camera** is focused on convenience - you'll trade some functionality of a full fledged camera to be able print photos on the spot:\n- You cannot use attachments with Instant Camera, other than built-in Flash.\n- Zooming is limited.\n- Shutter speed control is limited.\n- Resolution of the resulting images are a bit lower (configurable)\n\n</details>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n\n<h1><a href=\"https://moddedmc.wiki/project/exposure\">Wiki</a></h1>\n<br>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n\n\n[<img alt=\"Discord Server\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mortuusars/resources/main/media/banners/discord.png\" width=500/>](https://discord.gg/FzHKGDW2et)\n\n<h1> </h1>\n\n#### Enjoying the mod? Your support would allow me to continue working on it and on other mods!\n[<img alt=\"Patreon\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mortuusars/resources/main/media/banners/patreon.png\" width=500/>](https://patreon.com/mortuusars?utm_medium=unknown&utm_source=join_link&utm_campaign=creatorshare_creator&utm_content=copyLink) [<img alt=\"PayPal\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mortuusars/resources/main/media/banners/paypal.png\" width=98/>](https://www.paypal.com/donate/?hosted_button_id=4VPMCBCLZVUEA)\n\n</div>",
