    "name": "FastBoot",
    "summary": "FastBoot is engineered to drastically reduce game loading time",
    "description": "### **FastBoot: Accelerate Your Game Loading Time**\n\n![banner](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/99ede3aa950f3d796158fbe182ddb017a0ff2e99_0.webp)\n\n‚ö° FastBoot is a mod that made to reduce game loading time, by using mixins overwrites on game loading stage\n\n## How It Works\n\nFastBoot operates on a simple idea: in most cases, data conversion and processing for every game version is unnecessary. \n\n_As a result, the game loading speed decreases.\nFastBoot has a similar approach as LazyDFu and Smoot Boot, but at the same time tries to maintain game stability and compatability with other mods_\n\n## üéÆ Tests\n\n‚ö° Several tests were made on all compatible versions (1.16.5 - 1.21.4). As a result, FastBoot helps to boost the game loading stage by 1.5x-2x times, compared to tests without the mod ‚ö° \n\nüé• Here's a video showcasing the mod's tests:\n\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/KQuwUAmp-tk\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n## üìä Stats\n\n### A table representing game loading times for different versions of Minecraft with and without FastBoot:\n\n_A table with the game loading times for different versions of Minecraft with and without FastBoot:_\n\n| Minecraft Version | Vanilla Loading Time | FastBoot Loading Time |\n|-------------------|----------------------|-----------------------|\n| 1.16.x            | 15 seconds           | 10 seconds            |\n| 1.17.x            | 28 seconds           | 10 seconds            |\n| 1.18.x            | 24 seconds           | 8 seconds             |\n| 1.19.x            | 16 seconds           | 8 seconds             |\n| 1.20.x            | 17 seconds           | 10 seconds            |\n\n## üîß Compatability\nThe mod works well with all other mods, including perfomance mods. FastBoot is fully compatable with OptiFine.",
