    "summary": "Adds 13 new armor trims to discover and collect",
    "description": "![Title](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/FGNYBAJ6/images/d6764b0378493bf69be056f7e3aa3e28e9c6ab33.png)\nIf you thought that there could be more armor trims in Minecraft, you are just like me! And this mod is definitely for you, it adds new armor trims to the game, that are quite hard to obtain.¬†Currently, ten new smithing templates added, but I am looking to add more.\n\n_Mod reqiures [Fabric API](https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api)._\n\n_For updates and teasers, you can join my [Discord Server](https://discord.gg/6d52nzVFJY) :D_\n\n![Storm and Ram Armor Trim](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/FGNYBAJ6/images/68eb54823c0cc597f13e3085f8711334718fa7d0.png)\n\n![Myth and Greed Armor Trim](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/FGNYBAJ6/images/c0e5345a2629dc55bd3d2685a107f67aaea9f1b0.png)\n\n![Beast and Fever Armor Trim](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/FGNYBAJ6/images/f640b807d9e423476540541a34f4527902552812.png)\n\n![Wraith and Nihility Armor Trim](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/FGNYBAJ6/images/501bb414abd1959ee1ab71b73fce2b0f0ecabe25.png)\n\n![Horizon and Origin Armor Trim](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/FGNYBAJ6/images/77ead45cb07265b496c9c493e55ad854a0f7226d.png)\n\n![Twilight, Parasite and Witness Armor Trim](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/FGNYBAJ6/images/6c730ea55237fc3eba337bafd51bf8cdec79820a.png)\n\n<details>\n<summary>How to obtain</summary>\n\nStorm:\nCan be obtained through fishing during thunder, and comes with a treasure (33% chance)\n\nRam:\nKill a Ravager that has an Evoker as a passenger or an Evoker riding a Ravager\n\nMyth:\nCan be bought from Wandering Trader for 15 emeralds\n\nGreed:\nCan be found in badland mineshafts (20% chance)\n\nBeast:\nCan be found in igloo basement (50% chance)\n\nFever:\nCan be found in a ruined portal in the nether (20% chance)\n\nWraith:\nKill a Wither in the Soul Sand Valley biome\n\nNihility:\nDrops from a spawner in the Overworld (30% chance)\n\nHorizon:\nCan be found in suspicious gravel in cold ocean ruins (6% chance)\n\nOrigin:\nCan be found by sniffer in Old Growth Taiga (30% chance)\n\nTwilight:\nCan be found by a cat as a morning gift (11% chance)\n\nParasite:\nDrops from an endermite killed by an enderman (20% chance)\n\nWitness:\nDrops from a natural creaking heart during the night (20% chance)\n\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Localizations</summary>\n\nEnglish\n\nUkrainian\n\nPolish\n\nDeutch\n\nFrench\n\nItalian\n\nSimplified Chinese (by Balio & QZYMY)\n\nTraditional Chinese (by Balio)\n\nJapanese (by Abbage230)\n\nSpanish (by J4VY3R)\n\nKorean (by Parksidury2011)\n\nBrazilian (by inf3cted_w0lf)\n\n</details>\n\n![Other Projects](https://imgur.com/qJIVtFH.png)\n\n[![Mythic Charms](https://imgur.com/V0gVr5C.png)](https://modrinth.com/mod/mythic-charms)",
