    "name": "Palladium",
    "summary": "Another optimizing mod, provides deduplication, improved memory control, shader/chunk/nbt optimizations and enchanced mob AI.\n\nFull compatible with Sodium/Forks, Lithium/Forks, Iris/Forks",
    "description": "![fo](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8457cf2b01e18302ef61da3256328bfb4b94ad14.png)\n![fa](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6c152554bb3141433b6dca087131f96f00a876ba.png)\n![qu](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/554809ee9ae740db0707b7cd1420d937b490cd6b.png)\n![neo](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5d6378864df2d8f2699289ec7f439e26b5c8db60.png)\n</br>\n![i](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ca0de18375553419eff9ce315dccceb885971010.png)\n![pull](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/702dd4310f1da518cfe1eb65953281f022b75e05.png)\n</br>\n**Tests on 1.20.2 without any optimizing mods.**\n</br>\n</br>\nVanilla:\n![1](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/dd2b33532dcd51c4cf5cbcef02a5288bf9579f88.png)\nPalladium:\n![2](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/33a5b8f599a3a0a1a9e377854979a3ed098accc6.png)\n\n**World loading/creation time(seconds) comparison table(1.1.1+):**\n|  | Vanilla | Palladium |\n|--------------|-----------|-----|\n| World creation  | 08.92 | 08.06 |\n| World loading   | 02.96  | 02.71 |\n\n# Features ‚≠ê:\n\n**Deduplication - Removes duplicates of:**\n- Resource key\n- Resource location\n- Verticies\n\n**Mob AI:**\n<br/>\nImprove cat and wolf attack AI\n<br/>\nImprove wolf and rabbit flee AI\n\n**Shaders:**\n<br />\nMod caches uniforms, shaderi's, shaderi logs of shaders, reducing the number of times they are invoked.\n<br />\nFull compatible with Sodium/Forks, Lithium/Forks, Iris/Forks ~~and shader-packs~~ the shaders work but with bugs, I'm working on it...\n\n**Chunk building optimization:**\n<br />\nOptimizes work with chunks.\n<br />\nThe results are in the table above.\n\n**NBT optimization:**\n<br />\nSlightly improves work with the main storage file format(.nbt)\n\nAnd a few more minor fixes/improves...\n\n# FAQ\n\nQ: Do you plan to release palladium on [insert version or loader]? \n<br />\nA: Palladium will be 100% available over time on versions 1.20 and above on:\n- neoforge\n- quilt\n- fabric\n- forge(<1.21)\n<br />\n\nQ: Curseforge release?\n<br />\nA: Maybe, when I have a little more free time.\n\nQ: The mod does not give the effect as in the tests, why, is it cheating?\n<br />\nA: The effect depends on the number of mods, pc configuration and much more, do not expect that it will be identical to the tests above.\n\nQ: Will you support 1.20 or any other version when it becomes obsolete? \n<br />\nA: Yes, there will be bug-fixes for sure, but the priority will be lower than popular versions.\n\nQ: Updates take a long time to come out, why is that?\n<br />\nA: At the moment, in addition to GPUTape, H+, Palladium and ToadLib, I have two rather large mods, and I work on all of them alone.\n\n**Available languanges: üåê**\n- English(en_us) - Mr.Toad\n- Russian(ru_ru) - Mr.Toad, mpustovoi\n- Traditional Chinese(zh_tw, partial on 1.1+) - yichifauzi\n- German(de_de, partial on 1.1+) - NextRaven10\n- Turkish(tr_tr) - MissionWAR\n- Ukrainian(uk_ua) - StarmanMine142\n- Mexican Spanish(es_mx) - TheLegendofSaram\n<br/>\nWant to add localization? Welcome to github-pulll requests!\n\nFor in game config(<1.1.0): \n- on forge needs embeddium 0.3.20+.\n- on neoforged needs embeddium\n- on fabric/quilt needs sodium\n</details>\n\nOther my mods:\n- [H+](https://modrinth.com/mod/h_plus)(Hardcore improve)\n- [EnlightenedBlockEntities/EBEReforged](https://modrinth.com/mod/ebe-forge)(Fork of enchanced block entities)[DISCONTINUED]\n- [GPUTape](https://modrinth.com/mod/gputape/)(Optimizing)\n- [MovieMaker](https://modrinth.com/mod/moviemaker)(Content)",
