    "slug": "particular-reforged",
    "name": "Particular ‚ú® Reforged",
    "summary": "Particular is a mod that enhances Minecraft's ambience with many hand-crafted visual effects.",
    "description": "![](https://i.imgur.com/orqktjl.png)\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Particular is a mod that enhances Minecraft's ambience with many hand-crafted visual effects.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Support on [Discord](https://discord.gg/m4EHeRjfZ9) !</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n\n## Visual Effects\n\n*   [3D water splashes](https://youtu.be/vdrn4ouZRvQ?t=27)\n    *   Matches the water color\n    *   The wider the entity the wider the splash\n    *   The taller the fall the taller the splash\n\n![](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1219053/description_4678497c-2509-47c8-aa19-264ab655e858.png)\n\n*   Waterfall cascades\n    *   Cascades appear when falling water is over 2 block deep source water and the top source water has at least 1 open side\n    *   Cascade strength is proportional to the falling water's height and the number of open sides to the source water\n\n![](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1219053/description_37321349-afcb-445f-bf8b-97adc123e676.png)\n\n*   Fireflies\n    *   Spawn in warm biomes at flowers and tall grass\n    *   Spawn rates are randomized at dusk\n\n![](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1219053/description_79f6f459-600e-4f0d-83ad-6d8dbbffff54.png)\n\n*   Falling leaves\n    *   Each leaves block has a unique leaf particle with varying behavior\n    *   Creates ripples when landing on water\n\n![](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1219053/description_a900b786-5bcc-46fe-8183-f8776d5da629.png)\n\n*   Cave dust\n    *   Spawn rates are proportional to depth and sunlight level\n\n![](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1219053/description_1a888eaa-9012-4c41-8528-330f073c9cdd.png)\n\n*   Bubbles from underwater chests and barrels\n    *   When a chest or barrel is opened underwater it releases bubbles\n    *   Ender chests release green-tinted bubbles\n    *   Place soul sand under a chest to make it automatically open and release bubbles\n\n![](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1219053/description_13325853-dcbc-4489-941b-faca3092a063.png)\n\n*   Popping bubbles\n*   Ripples from rain and water drips\n*   Cake eating particles\n*   Emissive lava drips\n\n## Configuration\n\nThe mod can be configured to disable any of the effects and adjust which biomes should not spawn cave dust.\n\n## Supported Mods\n\n*   [Traverse](https://www.modrinth.com/mod/traverse)\n    *   Custom falling leaves\n*   [Regions Unexplored](https://www.modrinth.com/mod/regions-unexplored)\n    *   Custom falling leaves\n*   [Wilder Wild](https://www.modrinth.com/mod/wilder-wild)\n    *   Custom falling leaves\n\n## Supported Languages\n\n*   Canadian English (Voxxin)\n*   Canadian French (Voxxin)\n*   Chinese Simplified (KlainsX)\n*   European French (Voxxin)\n*   Mexican Spanish (cerealconjugo)\n*   Russian (Alexander317)\n\n## Disclaimers\n\nPort of the [Fabric](https://modrinth.com/mod/particular) version.\n\n[Effective](https://modrinth.com/mod/effective)¬†is a similar but unrelated mod that's available for older versions and Built for Quilt‚Ñ¢, so send them some love!\n\n¬†\n\nIf you'd like to support me and the development of my mods, I recommend trying out BisectHosting. Use code \"project8gbderam\" to get 25% off your first month of a gaming server for new customers. They offer 24/7 support and lightning-fast response times, ensuring you're in great hands and providing exceptional assistance for all your gaming needs.¬†[https://www.bisecthosting.com/project8gbderam](https://www.curseforge.com/linkout?remoteUrl=https://www.bisecthosting.com/project8gbderam)\n\n![Bisect](https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/54bb107c-f9fc-4f32-8515-fb4e3d56c124.png)",
