    "slug": "smsn",
    "name": "Save My Shaky Network",
    "summary": "Block common mods from connecting to the internet without affecting the mods' functionality, preventing slow loading or game crashes caused by network issues.",
    "description": "Block common mods from connecting to the internet without affecting the mods' functionality, preventing slow loading or game crashes caused by network issues.\n\n![Forge 1.20.1](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/23537730e2fb0303989f7306a3bb13201cec4e2c.png)\n\n## Why This Mod Exists\n\nBecause in certain regions with strict network censorship, accessing specific websites is impossible. For example, in China, websites like Patreon and GitHub are blocked and cannot be accessed normally. However, some popular mods, such as Quark, have included code that requests these websites, and when these requests fail, it can cause the game to stutter or crash. These issues typically occur during server startup or when players join. This mod was created to solve this problem by blocking such network requests, improving game stability for players in affected regions.\n\n- [Quark#3160](https://github.com/VazkiiMods/Quark/issues/3160)\n- [Quark#3331](https://github.com/VazkiiMods/Quark/issues/3331)\n- [Quark#3416](https://github.com/VazkiiMods/Quark/issues/3416)\n- [ÂÖ≥‰∫éÂ§∏ÂÖãÊ®°ÁªÑ‰∏ÄÁõ¥Â∞ùËØïËøûÊé•Ëá≥PatreonÁöÑÈóÆÈ¢ò](https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV14E421u7Kt/)\n- [Ëß£ÂÜ≥QuarkÊ®°ÁªÑÊó†Ê≥ïÂä†ËΩΩËµûÂä©ËÄÖ‰ø°ÊÅØÊó†ÈôêÊä•ÈîôÁöÑÈóÆÈ¢ò](https://www.bilibili.com/read/cv13814407/)\n\nA few months ago, I noticed that my Minecraft server was taking nearly 10 minutes to start each time. After investigating, I discovered that Quark was causing this issue. Upon searching the issue tracker, I found that the author of Quark refused to address this problem, which led me to develop this mod to resolve it.\n\n## Features\n\nFor Forge/NeoForge: Set `versionCheck = false` in `config/fml.toml` to disable the loader's update checker.  \nFor Fabric with ModMenu: Set `\"update_checker\": false` in `config/modmenu.json` to disable ModMenu's update checks.\n\n- [1.20.1 features](https://github.com/gizmo-ds/smsn-mod/tree/1.20.1?tab=readme-ov-file#features);\n- [1.18.2 features](https://github.com/gizmo-ds/smsn-mod/tree/1.18.2?tab=readme-ov-file#features);\n- [1.19.2 features](https://github.com/gizmo-ds/smsn-mod/tree/1.19.2?tab=readme-ov-file#features);\n- [1.21.1 features](https://github.com/gizmo-ds/smsn-mod/tree/1.21.1?tab=readme-ov-file#features);\n- [1.21.6, 1.21.7, 1.21.8 features](https://github.com/gizmo-ds/smsn-mod/tree/1.21.6?tab=readme-ov-file#features).\n\n## F.A.Q\n\n1. Will XX Minecraft version be supported?  \n   The author can only guarantee maintenance for current mainstream versions and versions the author actively plays.\n2. Can I include `Save My Shaky Network` in a modpack?  \n   ‚úÖ Yes! It's recommended to\n   use [Modrinth .mrpack](https://support.modrinth.com/en/articles/8802351-modrinth-modpack-format-mrpack) or CurseForge\n   modpack ZIP format.  \n   ‚ùå Do not directly include the mod binary (`.jar`) in your modpack‚Äîprioritize user security.\n\n## License\n\nThis mod is distributed under [MIT license](https://github.com/gizmo-ds/smsn-mod/blob/1.20.1/LICENSE)",
