    "summary": "Seasons with changing colors, shifting temperatures, and more!",
    "description": "<center>\n\n![Serene Seasons Logo](https://i.imgur.com/l4lO6VR.png)\n\n[![Follow on Bluesky](https://i.imgur.com/NbcP2yr.png)](https://bsky.app/profile/glitchfiend.bsky.social) [![Follow on X](https://i.imgur.com/WNmQOhb.png)](https://x.com/Glitchfiend) [![Join our Discord](https://i.imgur.com/N7eZOt0.png)](https://discord.gg/GyyzU6T)\n\n[![Support on Patreon](https://i.imgur.com/ai6ZV95.png)](https://www.patreon.com/Adubbz) [![Donate via PayPal](https://i.imgur.com/rEoNmyV.png)](https://www.paypal.com/donate/?business=AdubbzG@gmail.com&cy_code=USD)\n\n</center>\n\n## Description\n\n#### Serene Seasons is a Minecraft mod that adds seasons. Grass and foliage colors will change throughout the year, and in the winter, temperatures will shift and allow for snow to fall in some biomes that don't normally receive any. Seasons also affect various other features, like crop growth, weather, and more!\n\n## Info and Terms\n\n### Requires [![GlitchCore Icon](https://i.imgur.com/zC7XoOh.png)](https://modrinth.com/mod/glitchcore) [GlitchCore](https://modrinth.com/mod/glitchcore) for Minecraft 1.20.4 and above*!  Also requires [Fabric API](https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api) for Fabric version.\n_*Also required for 1.20.1 on mod version 9.1.0.0 and above_\n\n*You may include this mod in a Modrinth-hosted modpack as long as you do not rehost the mod and only use builds uploaded directly by us, you do not sell the modpack or additional access to the mod via any means, and you follow any and all terms listed in the license for the version of the mod you are using.*\n\n## More by Glitchfiend\n\n[![Biomes O' Plenty Logo](https://i.imgur.com/HQ2opH6.png)](https://modrinth.com/mod/biomes-o-plenty) [![Tough As Nails Logo](https://i.imgur.com/r0ZlRwr.png)](https://modrinth.com/mod/tough-as-nails)",
