    "slug": "visible-traders",
    "name": "Visible Traders",
    "summary": "A mod that allows the player to view locked villager trades",
    "description": "<div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <center>\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=1YnWcxpQqnYdLR1KM3IbZD7inq8oHgVJ1\"  alt=\"Visible Traders Logo\">\n<h2>\n<b>A mod that allows the player to view locked villager trades</b>\n</h2>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/visible-traders\">\n<img alt=\"modrinth\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/modrinth_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Ramixin/VisibleTraders\">\n<img alt=\"github\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/github_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n<br>\n<img alt=\"fabric\" height=\"40\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/compact/supported/fabric_vector.svg\">\n<img alt=\"no forge\" height=\"40\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/compact/unsupported/forge_vector.svg\">\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=1mHxin-HqsIWkLe6Puz790VlVu-3RJEeV\"  alt=\"neoforge\">\n</center>\n</div>\n\n*Version 0.0.1 has been removed due to worlds not being upgradable to 0.0.2 once used and several other issues*\n\n# Does this mod support trade cycling mods?\nVisible Traders currently only supports [Trade Cycling by henkelmax](https://modrinth.com/mod/trade-cycling). If you want to see more compatible mods, reach out to the mod dev and see if they are interested in compat and have them contact Ramixin\n\n# The trades aren't generating on my Vanilla/Paper/Spigot/Bukkit server!\nVisible Traders is a mod that is requried on both the client and server in order to fuction. Since Vanilla, Paper, Spigot, Bukkit, and other servers do not support mods natively, the mod can not function in such environments. Please switch to a Fabric/NeoForge server\n\n# HELP! My game is crashing because of `compatibility level JAVA_21`!!!!!!\n\nVisible Traders was built using Java 21 (which is different than the Minecraft version). If you are getting this error, then that means you have an older version of Java installed on your computer. You need to install a newer version of Java to play with Visible Traders (or use any Minecraft version 1.21+). You can get an updated version from here: https://adoptium.net/temurin/releases/\n\n# Does this work with modded villagers?\n\n---\nYes! This mod is fully compatible with all villager types.\n\n# What if I had villagers before I used this mod? Will it work?\n\n---\nYes again! This mod will make sure any villager existing before this mod is installed will display their trades as well.\n\n# What if I install the mod, and then remove it. What will happen?\n\n---\nIf removed, the locked trades that Visible Traders generates will also be removed to prevent villagers from instantly having all of their trades unlocked.\n\n## License\n\n---\nThis project is under an MIT license",
