    "description": "[![CF downloads](https://cf.way2muchnoise.eu/waterframes.svg?badge_style=for_the_badge)](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/waterframes)\n[![CF current version](https://img.shields.io/curseforge/v/834607?style=for-the-badge&label=curseforge&labelColor=2d2d2d&color=e04e14)](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/waterframes/files)\n[![Minecraft versions supported](https://cf.way2muchnoise.eu/versions/Supports_waterframes_all.svg?badge_style=for_the_badge)](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/waterframes/files)\n[![Discord server](https://dcbadge.limes.pink/api/server/https://discord.gg/cuYAzzZ)](https://discord.gg/cuYAzzZ)\n\n<h1 style=\"color:#eb622b\"><strong>üñºÔ∏è WATERFrAMES | MULTIMEDIA DISPLAYS</strong></h1>\n\nYour mod for image displaying, show pictures, videos, gifs and more in multiple and unique blocks, using URLs and a confortable interface to rotate, set transparency, brightness, or the audio distance, display your videos with a confortable experience, synchronized with you and your friends and fully designed to work for server-admins and in survival mode.\n\nHeavily inspired in [LittlePictureFrames](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/littleframes)\n\n[Join to my discord community](https://discord.gg/cuYAzzZ), and share your screenshots of you and your friends watching movies or memes, and your cinema buildings.\n\n<h1 style=\"color:#eb622b\"><strong>üéÅ CONTENT OF THE MOD</strong></h1>\n\n- üì∫ Multiple ways to show images (Frames, Projectors, TVs and Big TVs)\n- üéÆ Items (Remote Control) and commands (`/waterframes`) to control the frames from far away\n- üìÇ Local files support _(powered by WATERMeDIA)_ using `water://local/<path>`\n- üì∫ VideoPlayer support\n- üîó Compatible with Youtube, Twitch, Kick.com, Google Drive, One Drive, Twitter (X) and \\[orange\\_page\\]\n- üõ°Ô∏è Good managment for server admins (url whitelist, gamemode permissions, etc)\n- ‚öôÔ∏è Fully customizable and configurable image (rotation, transparency, brightness and more)\n- ‚è±Ô∏è Easy to use and compatible with other mods having video support (WATERMeDIA)\n\n<h1 style=\"color:#eb622b\"><strong>üß© DEPENDENCIES</strong></h1>\n\n- [CreativeCore](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/creativecore): GuiAPI and Networking\n- [WATERMeDIA](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/watermedia): Multimedia Support\n\n<h1 style=\"color:#eb622b\"><strong>üñ•Ô∏è SHOWCASE VIDEO (ENGLISH)</strong></h1>\n\n<span><span><span><span><span><span><span><iframe src=\"https://youtube.com/embed/Dfy0mYqblms?si=r1Cy_ZnKWjE8-wzB&amp;t=14\" width=\"840\" height=\"400\"></iframe></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\n\n<h1 style=\"color:#eb622b\"><strong>üñ•Ô∏è SHOWCASE VIDEO (ESPA√ëOL)</strong></h1>\n\n<span><span><span><span><span><span><span><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/jbi1uoL4Bmk\" width=\"840\" height=\"400\"></iframe></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\n\n<h1 style=\"color:#eb622b\"><strong>üïπÔ∏è PLAY WITH YOU AND YOUR FRIENDS</strong></h1>\n\n**Get a server at just 1$ to get a 15% discount and make a theater with your friends** [![KineticHosting sponsor code WATERMoDS](https://i.imgur.com/2WFmJzc.png)](https://www.kinetichosting.net/)\n\n<h1 style=\"color:#eb622b\"><strong>‚ÅâÔ∏è FAQ</strong></h1>\n\n- ¬øHow can I play local files?\n  - Modpacks can use a relative path using a `water://local/<path>`, root is the modpack folder, so if you place your modpack intro in `config/mymodpack/video.mp4` you must replace `<path>` with that path\n- ¬øCan you backport to 1.16.5?\n  - No, I refuse to go under 1.18.2. I am open for commisions for it but it has a high price.\n- Can keep maintaining the Fabric port for 1.21.4?\n  - No, fabric was a headache since I started the port, and for the good sake of my mental sanity, I stopped maintaining it.\n- When I put a video, block shows a picture saying \"Failed to Load VLC\"\n  - If you run on Linux or Mac, you must install VLC manually, if you run on windows or you already installed VLC on the mentioned OS please [submit a issue here](https://github.com/WaterMediaTeam/watermedia)\n\n<h1 style=\"color:#eb622b\"><strong>üéÄ SPECIAL THANKS TO</strong></h1>\n\n- [**Wayerspork**](https://lifeonlinesphere.com/): Donator and active bug reporter/helper\n- **Kotyarendj**: Author of the current WATERFrAMES block textures\n- [**CoolDCB**](https://github.com/CoolDCB): Helping me backporting LittleFrames and motivating me to make my own mod\n- [**CreativeMD**](https://github.com/CreativeMD): For making LittleFrames inspiriting me. Having me patience on the PRs and begin a nice dude.",
